{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_06_01",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri001.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、本当にダンサーに戻る気はないの？\nこれからもアイドルとして踊り続けるの？",
      "startTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。今はアイドルの方が楽しいから\n……それに、一緒に踊りたい仲間がいるから",
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数週間前。テレビ番組の収録スタジオ",
      "startTime": 20.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ収録が始まるのに、怜はどこに行ったんだ？\n……ん？　あれは……怜が誰かと話しているのか？",
      "startTime": 27.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "久しぶりね。会うのはいつ以来かしら",
      "startTime": 34.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "台本を見たらあなたの名前があって驚いたわ\n有名アーティストのバックダンサーなんて凄いじゃない",
      "startTime": 43.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あなたがこんなに頑張ってたなんて\n全然知らなかった",
      "startTime": 49.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri002.m4a",
      "text": "知らなかった？　大人気アイドル様は\n私のことなんて眼中になかったってこと？",
      "startTime": 55.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri003.m4a",
      "text": "しばらく会わないうちに、怜は随分偉くなったのね",
      "startTime": 59.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "え……？",
      "startTime": 63.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri004.m4a",
      "text": "人気が出たからって\nいい気にならないでほしいわ",
      "startTime": 67,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな……私はいい気になってなんか……",
      "startTime": 69.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri005.m4a",
      "text": "悪いけど、あんたなんかとお喋りする気はないから\nそれじゃ、私はもう行くわ",
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.333333399989,
          "startTime": 79.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、エリカ……",
      "startTime": 80.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（今のは怜の知り合いか？）\n（それにしては険悪な雰囲気だったが……）",
      "startTime": 87.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、いつからそこに？\nもしかして、見てたんですか？",
      "startTime": 96.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。覗き見するつもりはなかったんだ\nそれより今の子は？",
      "startTime": 102.4333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "彼女は平島エリカ。昔のダンス仲間です\n……と言っても、それほど親しい訳じゃないんですけど",
      "startTime": 110.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "エリカとはダンスの大会で何度も顔を合わせるうちに\n話をするようになったんです",
      "startTime": 119.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "エリカの実力は同年代の中ではずば抜けていて\n私が優勝した大会でも彼女が優勝の最有力候補でした",
      "startTime": 126.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "怜のライバルだったんだな",
      "startTime": 131.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "はい。友達と言うより、お互いに実力を認め合った\n切磋琢磨するライバルとして見ていました",
      "startTime": 139.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを認めてくれていた彼女が\nどうしてあんな態度を……",
      "startTime": 146.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "きっと何か誤解しているんだ。話せば分かってくれるさ",
      "startTime": 148.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "誤解……そうですよね\n話せばきっと分かってくれますよね",
      "startTime": 157.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "startTime": 161.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.1
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、少しいいですか？",
      "startTime": 164.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ？　元気がないが何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 168.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "実は、エリカともう一度話そうと思って\n彼女の所に行ったんですが……",
      "startTime": 176.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri006.m4a",
      "text": "しつこいわよ、さっきから一体何様のつもり？",
      "startTime": 181.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "私はただ、頑張ってるエリカを応援したくて……",
      "startTime": 186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_01-hiraeri007.m4a",
      "text": "それが上から目線だって言ってるの。ちょっと人気が\n出たからって調子に乗って、ウザいんだけど",
      "startTime": 193.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
